Name
       timing_enable_genclk_divide_by_inherit_parent_duty_cycle

Syntax
       timing_enable_genclk_divide_by_inherit_parent_duty_cycle

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Controls  inheritance  of  duty  cycle  from master clock for generated
       clocks (generated using the create_generated_clock  -divide_by  parame-
       ter).

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

